    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>User Story:</b> <em>As a Stakeholder, I want to see our progress visualized so that I can assess if our 5-day sprint cycle is sustainable.</em></li>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b> Update the Jira/GitHub project board daily. Generate the Burndown chart for the Sprint 2 Review.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> Burndown chart shows a clear "Actual" line compared to the "Ideal" line.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

