    <table cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" align="center">
    <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#bbbbbb" width="1%" nowrap align="center">
            &nbsp;<font color="#ffffff"><b>Description</b></font>&nbsp;
        </td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    </table>

    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>User Story:</b> <em>As a Student, I want to see a list of my previously submitted articles on my phone so that I can check the status of my entries while on the go.</em></li>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b>
	<ul>
		<li>Design a responsive "Card-based" list for mobile views and a "Table-based" list for desktop.</li>
		<li>Include status badges (e.g., "Pending," "Under Review," "Closed").</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria (UoG Alignment):</b>
	<ul>
		<li>The design utilizes <b>Lucide-React</b> icons for visual cues (e.g., a "File" icon for docs, an "Image" icon for photos).</li>
		<li>Layout must demonstrate "Suitability for all devices" (Task 1 requirement).</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

