        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    </table>

    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>User Story:</b> <em>As a Student, I want the Terms and Conditions to be presented clearly before I submit so that I am fully aware of my intellectual property rights.</em></li>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b>
	<ul>
		<li>Design a dedicated T&amp;C modal or page with a "Force Scroll" or clear checkbox mechanism.</li>
		<li>Ensure the typography is optimized for readability (line height, font size).</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria (UoG Alignment):</b>
	<ul>
		<li>The design includes a "Print" or "Download" option for the T&amp;Cs (a common UoG usability expectation).</li>
		<li>Visual feedback is provided when the user agrees (e.g., the "Submit" button changes from disabled to primary color).</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

