    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>User Story:</b> <em>As a Mobile User, I want the file upload button and T&amp;C modal to be clickable on my small screen so that I can submit my work from my phone.</em></li>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b> Test the "Submission Wizard" (built by Thet Wai and designed by May Thin) on iOS/Android emulators and physical devices.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> No horizontal scrolling on the T&amp;C modal. The "Drag &amp; Drop" area converts to a clear "Select File" button on touch devices.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

