    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>User Story:</b> <em>As a Compliance Auditor, I want to verify that a submission cannot be created without a record of T&amp;C acceptance.</em></li>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b> Attempt to bypass the frontend and send a raw POST request to the API without the T&amp;C agreement flag.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> The backend must reject the request. In the DB, the <tt>TermsAgreements</tt> table must correctly link the <tt>SubmissionID</tt> to the <tt>Timestamp</tt>.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

