            <ul>
	<li><b>Scope:</b> Create <tt>TermsAgreements</tt> table to log <tt>UserId</tt>, <tt>TermsVersion</tt>, and <tt>AcceptedAt</tt>.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> Mandatory foreign key link to the <tt>Users</tt> table.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

