    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>User Story:</b> <em>As a Student, I want to see my dashboard populated with my previous articles so that I can confirm they were received by the university.</em></li>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b> Implement the <tt>useQuery</tt> hook to fetch data from Min Khant’s "My Submissions" API.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> The dashboard handles "Empty States" (e.g., "You haven't submitted anything yet") and "Loading States" with Shadcn Skeletons.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

