                <span style="font-size: 9px">(<a id="parent_issue_key" href="https://hhaheinms.atlassian.net/browse/EP-29">EP-29</a>)</span>
                <h3 class="formtitle"><img src="https://hhaheinms.atlassian.net/images/icons/link_out_bot.gif" width="16" height="16" />
