    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>User Story:</b> <em>As a Security Architect, I want to document how we store files safely so that we prove we have met the "Security Requirements" of the coursework.</em></li>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b> Write a 300-word justification on why files are stored outside the web root and how filenames are sanitized to prevent Path Traversal attacks.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> Included in the "Security" section of the Group Report draft.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
