    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <ul>
	<li><b>User Story:</b> <em>As a Student, I want the system's internal logic to be documented so that our group report meets the "Functionality" (10%) and "UML Diagrams" requirement.</em></li>
	<li><b>Technical Scope:</b> Create a detailed Usecase Diagram showing the interaction between the users and system which can easily visualize about the flow of web application to the stakeholders.</li>
	<li><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b> Diagram must clearly show the user roles and their permissions inside the application.</li>
</ul>

            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
